@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Health check with apiUrl variable
GET {{apiUrl}}

### GET all tasks
GET {{apiUrl}}/todos
Accept: application/json

### GET tasks with query (priority, completed, limit, offset, sortBy)
GET {{apiUrl}}/todos?priority=high&completed=false&limit=5&offset=0&sortBy=dueDate
Accept: application/json

### GET task by id
GET {{apiUrl}}/todos/1
Accept: application/json

### GET task by id (Error case: non-existent id)
GET {{apiUrl}}/task/100
Accept: application/json

### POST create task
POST {{apiUrl}}/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"title": "Tarea de prueba",
	"description": "Creada desde index.http",
	"priority": "medium",
	"completed": false,
	"dueDate": "2026-03-01T12:00:00.000Z",
	"tags": ["test","http"]
}

### PUT replace task (id = 1)
PUT {{apiUrl}}/todos/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"title": "Tarea actualizada",
	"description": "Reemplazada via PUT",
	"priority": "high",
	"completed": true,
	"dueDate": "2026-03-10T12:00:00.000Z",
	"tags": ["updated"]
}

### PATCH partial update (id = 1)
PATCH {{apiUrl}}/todos/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"completed": true
}

### DELETE task (id = 1)
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/todos/1



